    <who name="Peter Robinson">pbrobinson</who>
    <bug_when>2016-10-31 14:18:07 -0400</bug_when>
    <thetext>Does it work if you black list the sun4i_ss driver?

Add a file called /etc/modprobe.d/sun4i.conf

with the line:
blacklist sun4i_ss</thetext>
  </long_desc><long_desc isprivate="0" >
